                  </hi>. I am shopman to Mr. Travers—I received three saws, a bevil, and square, of the prisoner on the 30th of December, and the planes the next day.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. I bought the planes and two saws on the 30th of</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184101040060"></xptr>
